{"tid":1984083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"碧咸FB點名求助台灣家人們(好友粉絲):「請教如何健康、保持樂觀」","createTime":"2020-04-22T08:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T16:41:52.000Z","uid":14918,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9b8e8759ddde1b938139aff443578a6c21cbb64a","tid":1984083,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/img-0266-1587456680.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fimg-0266-1587456680.jpg&h=5b0d2ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貝克漢在臉書PO上他抱著愛犬的照片，右手玩弄著桌上的樂高，臉上看起來無奈又無聊，他寫到：<br />\n<br />\n4月18日這天，貝克漢也在臉書寫道：「這是英國進入隔離的第四星期，到目前為止我們組了樂高、下廚、看電影做運動，並試著做點工作。我知道你們都很有創意，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">我想請台灣的家人們給我一些建議，如何保持健美、正面並帶給大家歡樂。</span>在下面留言分享你的小撇步，我會挑一些我最愛的跟大家分享。保持健康並支持你的親人。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只有台灣人先睇到, 其他國家係睇唔到架<br />\nTVBS 都有報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uHQnMPld46Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuHQnMPld46Y&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CpS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=9f7d0530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uHQnMPld46Y</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vogue.com.tw/entertainment/article/davidbeckham-taiwan-isolationtips\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.com.tw%2Fentertainment%2Farticle%2Fdavidbeckham-taiwan-isolationtips&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CpS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=9ec03495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vogue.com.tw/entertainment/article/davidbeckham-taiwan-isolationtips</a>"},{"pid":"454fbb4990f3f26de40979534dcab3e93f832fa6","tid":1984083,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"應該請教下支那人沒事兒秘笈<img src=\"/assets/f